title: INSTYLER
description: As creators of the ORIGINAL 1-Way Rotating Iron and leaders in hair tool innovation, InStyler designs technologically advanced tools that make styling easier and more efficient while delivering amazing results. The InStyler’s family of products include the BLU Turbo Ionic Dryer, STRAIGHT UP Ceramic Straightening Brush, MAX 2-Way Rotating Iron, MAX WET TO DRY 2-Way Rotating Iron, TITANIUM 1-Way Rotating Iron, TULIP Auto Curler, IONIC STYLER Ceramic Hot Brush, and IONIC STYLER PRO Hot Brush & Ceramic Flat Iron.
